videos.headline: Louisville strikes first with red zone TD
videos.description: Louisville racks up the first points of the game as QB Micale Cunningham finds Marshon Ford in the flat for an easy seven-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Louisville strikes first with red zone TD) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: Louisville capitalizes on Syracuse's muffed punt
videos.description: Syracuse punt returner Sean Riley loses the ball and Louisville recovers to set up a 29-yard touchdown to Seth Dawkins on the very next play.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Louisville capitalizes on Syracuse's muffed punt) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: Cunningham keeps it himself for Louisville TD
videos.description: Louisville QB Micale Cunningham takes off from the pocket and scrambles down the sideline, scoring from 20 yards out for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cunningham keeps it himself for Louisville TD) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: Atwell gets behind defense for 90-yard TD
videos.description: Louisville QB Micale Cunningham goes deep to connect with a wide-open Tutu Atwell, who easily takes it to the house for a 90-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Atwell gets behind defense for 90-yard TD) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: Neal goes 45 yards untouched for Syracuse TD
videos.description: Syracuse RB Moe Neal bursts out the backfield and takes it all the way to the end zone for a 45-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Neal goes 45 yards untouched for Syracuse TD) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: Hall turns the corner for Louisville score
videos.description: Louisville's Hassan Hall gets to the edge and beats the defender to the pylon to score a 12-yard rushing touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hall turns the corner for Louisville score) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: Hawkins refuses to go down on 44-yard TD
videos.description: Louisville RB Javian Hawkins spins past multiple defenders at the line of scrimmage and then breaks free for a 44-yard touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hawkins refuses to go down on 44-yard TD) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: Cunningham tosses 5th TD to cap Louisville's win
videos.description: Louisville QB Micale Cunningham throws his fifth touchdown pass of the day to Tutu Atwell as the Cardinals put up 56 points against Syracuse.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cunningham tosses 5th TD to cap Louisville's win) 2019/11/23
